 Netflix 的这部新剧被称为恐怖主题版《继承之战》 https://www.nme.com/news/tv/this-new-netflix-show-being- Called-horror-version-of-succession-3513305?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=this-new-netflix-show-被称为恐怖版的继承Elizabeth AubreyWed, 11 Oct 2023 19:33:27 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3513305 <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Netflix 亚瑟之家" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该剧演员阵容强大，包括马克·哈米尔，获得了评论家的积极评价</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/this-new-netflix-show-being-called-horror-version-of-succession-3513305">这部新的 Netflix 节目被称为“继承之战”的恐怖主题版本，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Netflix 亚瑟之家" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Fall-of-the-House-of-Usher-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nerflix">Netflix</a>的新剧<em>《厄舍屋的倒塌》</em>迄今为止受到评论家的热烈欢迎，许多人将其形容为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/hbo">HBO</a>热门剧<em>《<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/succession">继承之战》</a>的恐怖版。</em></p><p>该剧是迈克·弗拉纳根 (Mike Flanagan) 的下一个项目，他创作了 Netflix 的<em>《鬼屋》</em> 、 <em>《鬼屋》</em>和今年的<em>《午夜弥撒》</em> 。</p><p>这部八集剧集讲述了制药巨头罗德里克·厄舍（布鲁斯·格林伍德饰演）和他富有的家族的悲惨垮台，他们经常不和——就像<em>《继承之战》</em>的演员们一样。</p><p>弗拉纳根去年在 X/ <a href="https://twitter.com/flanaganfilm/status/1469026606781849601" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>上描述该剧时写道：“这部迷你剧是埃德加·爱伦·坡一些最具标志性作品的现代混音版。为了讲述这个关于贪婪、恐怖和悲剧的史诗故事，我们召集了无畏影业历史上最庞大的演员阵容。”</p><p>该剧于 10 月 12 日在 Netflix 首播，并获得<a href="https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/the_fall_of_the_house_of_usher/s01" target="_blank" rel="noopener">烂番茄</a>认证为“新鲜”，目前好评率高达 92%。 </p><p><iframe title="厄舍宫的倒塌|官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yvuAWVzP6wI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p> 《厄舍屋的倒塌》是迈克·弗拉纳根迄今为止最雄心勃勃的恐怖故事， <em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.theverge.com/23906083/the-fall-of-the-house-of-usher-movie-review-netflix" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《边缘》杂志评论道，</a></em>而<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;"><a href="https://ew.com/tv/tv-reviews/the-fall-of-the-house-of-usher-review-netflix-mike-flanagan/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《娱乐周刊》</a></em>则将其描述为“《 <em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">继承之战</em>》与埃德加·爱伦·坡同人小说的结合。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2023/10/the-fall-of-the-house-of-usher-netflix-review" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《名利场》</em></a>补充道：“《<em>厄舍屋</em>》是一部沉重的剧，充满了病态的幽默和阴郁的悲伤，政治暗示与无数流行文化的参考混杂在一起。该剧共八集，有时会让人筋疲力尽。然而，它自始至终都引人入胜，从哥特式转变为巴洛克式，每个亚瑟都受到悲惨的惩罚——一个接一个血淋淋的。”</p><p>与弗拉纳根的其他作品相比， <a href="https://metro.co.uk/2023/09/23/fall-of-the-house-of-usher-is-mike-flanagan-at-his-spooky-best-19517718/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>梅特罗</em></a>说：“ <em>《山庄闹鬼</em>》和<em>《午夜弥撒》</em>在磨练其更恐怖风格的同时，融入了戏剧的理念，而<em>《午夜俱乐部</em>》和《布莱<em>庄园闹鬼》则</em>颠覆了这一点，转而支持戏剧， <em>《厄舍屋的倒塌》</em>在一场扣人心弦、充满阴谋的表演中完美地融合了这两点。”</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://comicbook.com/tv-shows/news/you-season-4-review-joe-goldberg-keeps-getting-worse-and-the-netflix-series-keeps-getting-better/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Comicbook</em></a>表示这部作品“无法与弗拉纳根的前作相比”，但补充说，这部作品仍然有“巨大的……乐趣”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.empireonline.com/tv/reviews/the-fall-of-the-house-of-usher/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《帝国》</em></a>杂志认为这部剧“并不是对坡的改编”，并称它“更多的是对坡的自私和遗憾主题的诠释，被用作一个完全虚构的故事的基础。”</p><p>该剧演员阵容强大，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-hamill">马克·哈米尔</a>、威拉·菲茨杰拉德和玛丽·麦克唐纳，以及布鲁斯·格林伍德、卡拉·古奇诺、凯特·西格尔、亨利·托马斯、扎克·吉尔福德、卡尔·伦布利、萨曼莎·斯洛扬、特尼亚·米勒、拉胡尔·科利、迈克尔·特鲁科、安娜贝丝·吉什、罗伯特·朗斯特里特和凯蒂·帕克。</p><p>哈米尔（ <em>《星球大战》</em> ）将扮演“一个在阴影中出奇地自在的角色”，而麦克唐纳（《<em>太空堡垒卡拉狄加》</em> ）将扮演罗德里克的双胞胎妹妹玛德琳·亚瑟（Madeline Usher）。卡尔·卢布利（ <em>《睡眠医生</em>》）将饰演爱伦·坡的调查员 C.奥古斯特·杜平。</p><p>该剧将于 10 月 12 日星期四在 Netflix 首播。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/this-new-netflix-show-being-called-horror-version-of-succession-3513305">这部新的 Netflix 节目被称为“继承之战”的恐怖主题版本，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
